code: export async function fetchGif(searchTerm,setError){const API_KEY=process.env.GIPHY_API_KEY;console.log("API KEY",API_KEY);try{if(!searchTerm){throw new Error("Nothing has been searched");}const response=await fetch("https://api.giphy.com/v1/gifs/search?api_key=".concat(API_KEY,"&q=").concat(searchTerm,"&limit=5"));const data=await response.json();console.log("Returned",data);return data.data;}catch(error){console.error("Error fetching gif data:",error);setError(error.message);console.log("Error",error);return null;}}
